1 SECTION 2. The Ballot Title for the proposed Constitutional
2 amendment as set forth in SECTION 1 of this resolution shall be in
3 the following form:
4 BALLOT TITLE
5 Legislative Referendum No. ____ State Question No. ____
6 THE GIST OF THE PROPOSITION IS AS FOLLOWS:
7 This measure adds a new section to the State Constitution. It
8 adds Section 49 to Article 9 of the Oklahoma Constitution. It
9 protects private property rights by restricting eminent domain
10 for certain energy projects. It prohibits the use of eminent
11 domain for the siting or construction of wind turbines on
12 private property. It prohibits the use of eminent domain for
13 transmission lines that transmit electricity from wind energy
14 projects. It prohibits the use of eminent domain for
15 transmission lines associated with projects that receive
16 significant funding from the United States government. It
17 limits the use of eminent domain for federally subsidized wind
18 energy projects.
